data.description: **Open House 12/10 11-1PM**Welcome to your dream home! This stunning 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom single-story residence boasts 1,835 square feet of luxurious living space. Step inside and experience the epitome of modern comfort and style. The heart of this home is its beautiful kitchen, where culinary dreams come to life. Adorned with exquisite granite countertops, this space is not only aesthetically pleasing but also highly functional. Imagine preparing meals surrounded by the elegance of this well-designed kitchen. Stainless steel appliances add a touch of sophistication, providing both durability and a sleek, contemporary look. The spacious layout of this single-story gem ensures that every room is easily accessible and effortlessly flows from one to the next. The four bedrooms offer versatility, providing ample space for a growing family, a home office, or a guest room. With two tastefully appointed bathrooms, convenience is at the forefront of this home's design. Natural light floods the interior, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The open floor plan enhances the sense of space, making it perfect for both entertaining and everyday living. Whether you're hosting gatherings with friends or enjoying quiet family evenings, this home accommodates every lifestyle. Step outside to discover a well-manicured yard, offering the perfect setting for outdoor activities and relaxation. The curb appeal of this property is enhanced by its thoughtfully designed landscaping. Located in a desirable neighborhood, this home not only provides a sanctuary but also offers proximity to schools, parks, shopping, and other amenities.
